#. <section class="sutta" id="an7.83"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an7.83:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.83:0.2"
msgid "8. Vinayavagga"
msgstr "8. The Monastic Law"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an7.83:0.3"
msgid "83. Satthusāsanasutta"
msgstr "83. The Teacher’s Instructions"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an7.83:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā upāli yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ "
"abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā upāli bhagavantaṃ "
"etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then Venerable Upāli went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and "
"said to him:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an7.83:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Sādhu me, bhante, bhagavā saṅkhittena dhammaṃ desetu, yamahaṃ bhagavato "
"dhammaṃ sutvā eko vūpakaṭṭho appamatto ātāpī pahitatto vihareyyan”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Sir, may the Buddha please teach me Dhamma in brief. When I’ve heard it, I’"
"ll live alone, withdrawn, diligent, keen, and resolute.”"

msgctxt "an7.83:2.2"
msgid "“Ye kho tvaṃ, upāli, dhamme jāneyyāsi:"
msgstr "“Upāli, you might know that"

msgctxt "an7.83:2.3"
msgid ""
"‘ime dhammā na ekantanibbidāya virāgāya nirodhāya upasamāya abhiññāya "
"sambodhāya nibbānāya saṃvattantī’ti;"
msgstr ""
"certain things don’t lead solely to disillusionment, dispassion, cessation, "
"peace, insight, awakening, and extinguishment."

msgctxt "an7.83:2.4"
msgid "ekaṃsena, upāli, dhāreyyāsi:"
msgstr "You should definitely bear in mind that such things are"

msgctxt "an7.83:2.5"
msgid "‘neso dhammo neso vinayo netaṃ satthusāsanan’ti."
msgstr "not the teaching, not the training, and not the Teacher’s instructions."

msgctxt "an7.83:2.6"
msgid "Ye ca kho tvaṃ, upāli, dhamme jāneyyāsi:"
msgstr "You might know that"

msgctxt "an7.83:2.7"
msgid ""
"‘ime dhammā ekantanibbidāya virāgāya nirodhāya upasamāya abhiññāya "
"sambodhāya nibbānāya saṃvattantī’ti;"
msgstr ""
"certain things do lead solely to disillusionment, dispassion, cessation, "
"peace, insight, awakening, and extinguishment."

msgctxt "an7.83:2.8"
msgid "ekaṃsena, upāli, dhāreyyāsi:"
msgstr "You should definitely bear in mind that such things are"

msgctxt "an7.83:2.9"
msgid "‘eso dhammo eso vinayo etaṃ satthusāsanan’”ti."
msgstr "the teaching, the training, and the Teacher’s instructions.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.83:2.10"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
